Name: ModelicaRes
Version: 0.6.1
Summary: Utilities to set up and analyze Modelica simulation experiments
Home-page: http://kdavies4.github.com/ModelicaRes/
Author: Kevin Davies
Author-email: kdavies4@gmail.com
